race.comment: CHA CHA ETHICS (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 3 last run (17.45) at Richmond Straight. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Good form should continue. AIRFLOW BETTY (3) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 340m behind Upended (19.90) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Can do much better this time. NO SPARK LEFT (8) was a narrow winner last time, jumping from this same box to score by 0.8 lengths in a Grade 5 over 401m at Richmond. Expected to feature again. MARSA DOUGIE (4) placed last time and is worth some thought.
